{"tid":2498282,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登擬推出新一輪一萬億美元「美國家庭計畫」經濟刺激措施","createTime":"2021-04-21T05:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T05:17:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"629c51258e0aa4d9897ea30fe461c700668f69d4","tid":2498282,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕拜登3月底公佈規模達2.25兆美元的基礎建設計畫，消息人士向媒體透露，白宮預計在幾天內推出新1輪的經濟刺激計劃，規模達1兆美元（約28兆新台幣），推動兒童照護、延長兒童稅收抵免等家庭政策。<br />\n<br />\n《CNBC》報導，拜登政府擬接續被稱為「美國就業計畫（American Jobs Plan）」的基礎建設計畫，再推動第2階段的「美國家庭計畫（American Families Plan）」。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指出，這項家庭計畫尚未定案，預計將斥資1兆美元，其中包含5000億美元的稅務抵免。第2輪的經濟復甦預計將擴大兒童照護、有薪假、學前教育等措施，家庭計畫預計也將延長兒童稅收抵免至2025年。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3506602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3506602&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=ec6f3922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3506602&h=ebb73d81\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3506602</a>"},{"pid":"279b0eaf398be3d9cbd73dd04d6010705c7d63b5","tid":2498282,"uid":250073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T05:16:27.000Z","msg":"印完錢股票應該會再升？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f848f672ee885fd4dbfff9af3380ed6a62ae5a","tid":2498282,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"升到冇brake<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}